Image Version : v4.15
Release on    : 25/08/2023
Tag           : isharefoundation/ishare-satellite-app-mw:v4.15
Description   : 
  Change Request : 
    1. Handled the case-insensitive "OID" subject name search key.
    2. Parties endpoint with empty object handled


Update the latest image tag in the following steps
 Step 1: cd to the path of the middleware folder (/VM-Model-iSHARE-Satellites/middleware)
 Step 2: nano app-mw-config.yaml and added the below changes and save.
 Step 4: nano docker-compose-mw.yaml
 Step 5: Change the image version under "ishare_mw" (image: isharefoundation/ishare-satellite-app-mw:v4.15) docker service and save the file.
 Step 6: docker-compose -f docker-compose-mw.yaml up -d (To bring up the latest image up and running)


